ProductSkills is a PM skill pack at `{{PACKAGE_STORE}}`. There is no master workflow — this rule routes product work to the right skill based on the input artifact type. Read the canonical routing reference before invoking any skill:

`{{PACKAGE_STORE}}/references/routing/artifact-to-workflow.md`

## Routing

| Input artifact | Routed skill / workflow |
|---|---|
| Raw interviews / support / sales notes | **pm-discovery** (intake-triage → voc-synthesis) |
| Feature-request backlog needing routing | **pm-roadmap** (intake-triage) |
| Founder hypothesis, no evidence | **workflow-discovery-to-prd** (returns `decision_status: blocked` + research plan) |
| Synthesized research ready for PRD | **workflow-discovery-to-prd** |
| Opportunity or strategy note | **pm-strategy** (which bet) OR **pm-validation** (test assumption) |
| Rough PRD with gaps ("continue the workflow" framing) | **workflow-discovery-to-prd** (spec-reviews internally) |
| Standalone "review this PRD" request | **pm-docs** spec-review (one-shot) |
| Approved PRD ready for delivery | **workflow-prd-to-linear-delivery** |
| Delivery scope already split | **pm-delivery**; escalate to workflow-prd-to-linear-delivery for Linear preview |
| Launch request | **pm-gtm** launch-readiness |
| Post-launch metric / signal / experiment result | **pm-growth** experiment-readout / funnel-stage-analysis; **pm-gtm** post-launch-review |
| Decision needing durable record | **pm-docs/decision-memo** |
| Decision needing socialization | **pm-stakeholder-comms/decision-comms** |

If the input doesn't clearly match any row, **ask the user to clarify intent**; offer 2-3 most likely workflows from the table. Do not silently pick.

## Safety rules

- Do not invent customer evidence.
- Treat validation as routing, not mandatory replay.
- Use dry-run previews for Notion and Linear. Canonical safety contract: `{{PACKAGE_STORE}}/references/mcp/dry-run-preview.md`.
- Return blocked-workflow envelopes (`{{PACKAGE_STORE}}/schemas/blocked-workflow.schema.json`) when required inputs are missing; canonical resume target: `pm-discovery`.
- `pm-docs/postmortem` refuses SRE/ops incidents at intake.
- `pm-stakeholder-comms` refuses output unless `audience.tier` and `intent` are supplied.
